## Environment

- `AUTH_SECRET` — JWT signing key (required)
- `DATABASE_URL` — database connection (defaults to SQLite)
- `VELOIQ_AUTH_DISABLED=1` — disable auth enforcement in development
- Run `cp .env.example .env` in `backend/` before first start
